        correct: 1,
        rationale: "Chronic prednisone use suppresses the HPA axis. During surgery (a major physiological stress), these patients cannot mount an adequate cortisol response and are at risk for adrenal crisis. Stress-dose hydrocortisone must be administered perioperatively. Discontinuing steroids would be dangerous."
